Package core.tut.pori.dao.clause

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SQLClause
    The interface for implementing SQL Clauses.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndClause
    A simple SQL WHERE AND clause.
    AndSubClause
    Create and SQL sub-clause with AND prefix.
    JoinClause
    A class, which implements a simple SQL JOIN clause.
    OrClause
    A simple SQL WHERE OR clause.
    OrSubClause
    Create and SQL sub-clause with OR prefix.
    RawClause
    Create a raw sql WhereClause, the insertable sql string (such as COLUMN=? or COLUMN<9) can be added manually.
    UpdateClause
    This class defines a single SQL update clause.
    WhereClause
    Base class for SQL WHERE clauses.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SQLClause.SQLType
    Supported SQL types for the clause
    WhereClause.ClauseType
    Type of the WhereClause
